quran[7{c,v,t}:
42,45,aur tum un ko dekho ge ke dozakh ke samnay laaye jayen ge zillat se aajzi karte hue chhupi ( aur neechi ) nigah se dekh rahay hon ge. aur momin log kahin ke ke khasara uthany walay to woh hain jinhon ne qayamat ke din apne aap ko aur apne ghar walon ko khasaray mein dala. dekho ke be insaaf log hamesha ke dukh mein ( parre ) rahen ge
42,46,aur khuda ke siwa un ke koi dost nah hon ge ke khuda ke siwa un ko madad day saken. aur jis ko khuda gumraah kere is ke liye ( hadaayat ka ) koi rasta nahi
42,47,un se keh do ke ) qabal is ke ke woh din jo talle ga nahi khuda ki taraf se aa mojood ho apne perwar-digaar ka hukum qubool karo. is din tumahray liye nah koi jaye panah hogi aur nah tum se gunaaho ka inkaar hi ban parre ga
42,48,phir agar yeh munh phair len to hum ne tum ko un par nigehbaan bana kar nahi bheja. tumhara kaam to sirf ( ehkaam ka ) pouncha dena hai. aur jab hum ensaan ko apni rehmat ka maza chukhate hain to is se khush hojata hai. aur agar un ko un hi ke aamaal ke sabab koi sakhti pahunchti hai to ( sab ehsaanon ko bhool jatay hain ) be shak ensaan bara nashukara hai
42,49,( tamam ) badshahat khuda hi ki hai asmano ki bhi aur zameen ki bhi. woh jo chahta hai peda karta hai. jisay chahta hai betiyan ataa karta hai aur jisay chahta hai betay bkhshta hai
42,50,ya un ko betay aur betiyan dono inayat farmata hai. aur jis ko chahta hai be aulaad rakhta hai. woh to jan-nay wala ( aur ) qudrat wala hai
42,51,aur kisi aadmi ke liye mumkin nahi ke khuda is se baat kere magar ilham ( ke zariye ) se ya parday ke peechay se ya koi farishta bhaij day to woh khuda ke hukum se jo khuda chahay alqa kere. be shak woh aliiiii rutba ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
